To run the API 
Run The following commands

npm Install
npm install -g nodemon
nodemon

Then The database mongo db would be connected

The server will be started at localhost port number 3000.
Postman GET request would be posted Postman -> GET http://localhost:3000/news/fetchAndUpdate

Response:
Sources of top 10 headlines news from https://newsapi.org/

API called for fetching sources:
GET https://newsapi.org/v2/sources?apiKey=API_KEY

The same data will be saved in the MongoDB cloud.
